Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: topology: Return -ENOMEM on memory allocation failure
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: c173ee5b2fa6195066674d66d1d7e191010fb1ff
